`categories_description`: `These items represent the total products available to both our USA and Canadian Customers. Not all items are available in Canada.

`categories_id`: Anything with a silencer or Bullpup design cannot be brought into Canada. When in doubt please ask and we will be happy to look the item up for you. We will try to identify which items can be brought into Canada as time goes on.
A final shipping invoice will be sent for those orders not being picked up. We ship by Canada Post and only charge what they charge.

Finally, we place our orders on Tuesdays and they arrive to us by Monday ready for you to pickup or to be shipped. If for some reason we miss the delivery , worse case is the following Monday after that.

****PAL as with any firearms. If its over 500fps you will need the appropriate PAL to Match. Either Non-Restricted or Restricted. you will need to scan and email us a copy of the front and back before we place your order.`
